728042f-a.title: Queens: Steinway Street - Broadway
728042f-a.text:
Steinway Ste, (right) at the S.6. corner of Broadway (left), showing the Daufkirchs Astoria Gasino. In 1891 it was also known as Schnetzen Park. A group of four story structures occupied the site of this park
in 1928.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
